### **📡 AI at the Edge: Decentralized Intelligence**

✅ **Smartphones & AI** – Devices now run **speech recognition, facial authentication, and NLP models** natively.  
✅ **Autonomous Vehicles** – AI chips process **sensor fusion, object detection, and decision-making** in real-time.  
✅ **Smart Surveillance** – AI-powered cameras perform **live facial recognition and anomaly detection**.  
✅ **Wearable AI** – Devices like AI-powered hearing aids, smartwatches, and health monitors provide real-time analytics.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** AI at the edge increases **privacy risks, mass surveillance, and algorithmic discrimination** in public spaces.

**Related Notes:** [[algorithmic-policing]] | [[edge-ai-ethics]]

---

### **🔬 AI in Robotics & Industrial Automation**

✅ **AI-Powered Robotics** – AI enables **gesture recognition, object manipulation, and path planning** in robotics.  
✅ **AI in Manufacturing** – Predictive maintenance, defect detection, and automation of quality control.  
✅ **AI in Agriculture** – Smart tractors, AI-driven pest detection, and crop monitoring.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** AI-driven automation **displaces human labor**, disproportionately impacting marginalized workers.

**Related Notes:** [[automation-ethics]] | [[future-of-work-ai]]

